flowchart LR
  subgraph Core[Core matrix]
    R[Risk]
    S[Stage]
    FC[First control]
    O[Owner]
    P[Priority]
  end

  subgraph Team[Team worksheet]
    TID[Threat ID / domain]
    Goal[Attacker goal]
    Asset[Asset at risk]
    Signal[Detection signal]
    Impact[Impact + likelihood]
    Recovery[Recovery action]
  end

  Core -->|Expand only when teams need detail| Team

  Why1[Why it works<br/>Fast to explain and fast to prioritize]
  Why2[Use in engineering review<br/>when teams need fuller evidence]

  Core -.-> Why1
  Team -.-> Why2

  classDef stage fill:#e8f7ee,stroke:#22c55e,color:#14532d;
  classDef sheet fill:#eef2ff,stroke:#6366f1,color:#312e81;
  classDef note fill:#f8fafc,stroke:#94a3b8,color:#334155;

  class R,S,FC,O,P stage;
  class TID,Goal,Asset,Signal,Impact,Recovery sheet;
  class Why1,Why2 note;